id=dresosmicrog
name=DresOS microG
version=v3.0.1
versionCode=30001
author=DresOperatingSystems
description=Universal systemless microG suite. Ships the officially signed microG GmsCore 0.3.15, Companion and GsfProxy as privileged system apps under product, with a complete privapp-permissions allowlist generated from the bundled manifests, plus Aurora Store, Aurora Services and DroidGuard. Pure file overlay: no Zygisk payload, no Xposed, no runtime PackageManager work, and it never touches other modules, so it coexists with the DresOS AOSmium WebView module and cannot disable it. Signature spoofing is provided by the ROM: because the microG APKs carry the official microG key, any ROM with microG signature spoofing support (LineageOS 2024-02-26 and newer, e OS, CalyxOS, iodeOS, DivestOS and similar) spoofs them automatically once placed in priv-app. Refuses to install on GrapheneOS and where Google Play Services is already present. Android 8 through 16, all ABIs.
support=https://github.com/DresOperatingSystems/DresOS-Magisk-Modules/issues
updateJson=https://raw.githubusercontent.com/DresOperatingSystems/DresOS-Magisk-Modules/main/microg/update.json
minMagisk=24000
